      "widgets_values": [
        "A photo of three people in a bar. First, in focus, on the left is a ginger 24-year old girl named sarah with a round face, round cheeks, full lips, large expressive blue eyes and a turned up nose. Her make-up and lipstick has a natural and effortless look. She wears a casual grey tall-necked jumper.\nShe has chestnut colored, short wavy hair and subtle freckles on her cheeks. To the right is a an average looking, chubby, blonde woman in her thirties with a square face, a huge hawk nose, thin and cracked lips, a strongly cleft chin that protrudes and brown eyes with low and thin bleached eyebrows. She has short, unkempt hair and a short forehead. The two women are sitting around a table talking with a pint of lager besides each of them and are talking to each other and looking at each other. Behind them, out of focus at the bar is an elderly man with a wide face, greek nose and lots of wrinkles. All the people in the photo are visually distinct, with no resemblance or genetic relation with clearly unique facial features."
